The '''ASC 1846 Göttingen''' and its predecessor societies ''SSV Hellas Göttingen'' and ''SSC Göttingen'' played 16 times in the [[Basketball Bundesliga|Federal basketball league]] (1966–67, 1970–71, 1973–75 and 1976–88). The club became three times German champion and twice in a row [[German Basketball Cup|German Cup winner]].
The men's team of ASC Göttingen is currently playing in 1 Regionalliga Nord. Venue is the gym of the Georg-Christoph-Lichtenberg Comprehensive School; Main training venue is the sports hall of the Mountain Grove High School, where most of the other league matches will be played.
== Titles and achievements == '''[[Basketball Bundesliga|German League]]''' * '''Winners (3)''': 1979-80, 1982–83, 1983–84 '''[[German Basketball Cup|German Cup]]''' * '''Winners (2)''': 1983-84, 1984–85
