'''Hungary women's national bandy team''' is competing for [[Hungary]] in the international [[bandy]] tournaments. 

The team has so far only made appearances in two world championship tournaments, in [[Bandy World Championship for women 2007|2007]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bandysidan.nu/tavlinginfo.php?EVID=101&sprak=eng&land=3|title=World Championships Women 2006/07|publisher=Bandysidan|accessdate=February 12, 2014}}</ref> (as the host country) and [[Bandy World Championship for women 2008|2008]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bandysidan.nu/tavlinginfo.php?EVID=120&sprak=eng&land=3|title=World Championships Women 2007/08|publisher=Bandysidan|accessdate=February 12, 2014}}</ref> (in Sweden). It has lost all matches without scoring.

