'''Saraswoti Youth Club''' is a topflight [[association football]] club from [[Nepal]]. They play at 25,000 capacity [[Dasarath Rangasala Stadium]]. This club is from Koteshwor, Kathmandu; and has been one of the most competent and prominent football club from Nepal. Now, they are playing in 2018–19 Martyr's Memorial A-Division League.

