'''Visakha''' is a [[football (soccer)]] club in  [[Phnom Penh]], [[Cambodia]]. It plays in the [[Cambodian League]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/teams/cambodia/visakha/41977/|title=Cambodia - Visakha - Results, fixtures, squad, statistics, photos, videos and news - Soccerway|author=|date=|website=int.soccerway.com|accessdate=15 November 2018}}</ref> the top division of Cambodian football.

